    dc:creator "Stöhr, Sabine; Hugall, Andrew F.; Thuy, Ben; Martynov, Alexander" ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "Morphological diagnoses of higher taxa in Ophiuroidea (Echinodermata) in support of a new classification" ;
